OL,3,CLabour MP warns against 'draconian
OL,4,Ccuts' ahead of expected welfare reforms
OL,6,FA Labour MP has warned ministers
OL,7,Fagainst "draconian cuts" ahead of
OL,8,Fexpected changes to the welfare system.
OL,10,FRachael Maskell suggested she had
OL,11,Fdetected "deep, deep concern" from
OL,12,Fcolleagues in the Commons, amid risks
OL,13,Fof a rift between the Government and
OL,14,Fthe back benches.
OL,16,FReforms to the welfare system are
OL,17,Fexpected ahead of the Spring Statement
OL,18,Fat the end of this month, as Rachel
OL,19,FReeves will likely look to make a raft
OL,20,Fof public spending savings given
OL,21,Ftighter fiscal headroom.
