OL,3,CLabour MP warns against 'draconian
OL,4,Ccuts' ahead of expected welfare reforms
OL,6,FSpeaking to the BBC's Westminster Hour
OL,7,Fon Sunday, Ms Maskell, the MP for York
OL,8,FCentral, said that she has had a
OL,9,F"flurry of emails" from people who are
OL,10,F"deeply concerned" about the prospect
OL,11,Fof changes to the system.
OL,13,FShe told the programme: "We recognise
OL,14,Fthe economic circumstances that we're
OL,15,Fin and the hand that we were given and
OL,16,Fof course it is right that the
OL,17,FChancellor has oversight over all
OL,18,Fthose budgets but not at the expense
OL,19,Fof pushing disabled people into
OL,20,Fpoverty."
