OL,6,FShe added: "There's got to be a carrot
OL,7,Fapproach not a stick approach.
OL,9,F"We've got to make the right
OL,10,Finterventions and that doesn't start
OL,11,Fwith the stick."
OL,13,FMs Maskell said that she had "picked
OL,14,Fup (...) deep deep concern" from
OL,15,Fcolleagues and called for a
OL,16,F"compassionate system and not taking
OL,17,Fjust draconian cuts".
