OL,6,FDowning Street said on Friday that the
OL,7,F"broken security system is holding our
OL,8,Fpeople back".
OL,10,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,11,Fspokesman said that there has been an
OL,12,F""unsustainable rise in welfare
OL,13,Fspending", and added: "Left as it is,
OL,14,Fthe system we've inherited would
OL,15,Fcontinue to leave more and more people
OL,16,Ftrapped in a life of unemployment and
OL,17,Finactivity, and that's not just bad
OL,18,Ffor the economy, it's bad for those
OL,19,Fpeople too".
