OL,6,FThe shadow home secretary said on
OL,7,FSunday that the benefits system needs
OL,8,Fto be made tougher and claimed it is
OL,9,Ftoo easy for people to get welfare
OL,10,Fpayments.
OL,12,FSpeaking to Trevor Phillips on Sky
OL,13,FNews, Chris Philp said: "People are
OL,14,Fnow being able to be signed off
OL,15,Fbecause they've got anxiety and they
OL,16,Fare not having to even look for a job.
